english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}{code}{emphasisEnd} is your Roblox 2-Step Verification code for {emphasisStart}{accountName}{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Enter the above code into the 2-Step Verification screen to finish logging in. This code will expire in 15 minutes.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}This login request was received from {emphasisStart}{geoLocationInformation}{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好：{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}{code}{emphasisEnd} 是 {emphasisStart}{accountName}{emphasisEnd}的罗布乐思两步验证码。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}在两步验证窗口中输入上方显示的代码来完成登录。本代码将在 15 分钟之后失效。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}本次登录请求来自{emphasisStart}{geoLocationInformation}{emphasisEnd}。{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}感谢您的支持，{lineBreak}{emphasisStart} 罗布乐思团队{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer of the two step verification login email.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there was a Roblox login attempt from a new browser or device. If you did not make this request, you are strongly advised to change your password.

english: Hello {accountName},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This message is to notify you that our support team has deactivated 2-Step Verification with Authenticator for your Roblox account. This typically occurs due to a support ticket you submitted or as a security measure to ensure the safety of your account. A security code from an Authenticator app will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. You can reactivate 2-Step Verification in your {aTagStartWithHref}{AccountSettingsPageLink}{hrefEnd}account settings{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}If you need further assistance, {spanStartTagWithBold}do not reply to this email{spanEndTag}, and reply to your existing support ticket or submit a new support request here: {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox Support{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox
translation: {accountName} 您好，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我们的客服团队已为您的帐户停用两步验证。我们通常会因您提交的客服表格或为了确保您的帐户安全而采取此行动。当登录帐户或进行其他操作时，您将不再需要使用验证 App 的安全代码。您可以在{aTagStartWithHref}{AccountSettingsPageLink}{hrefEnd}帐户设定{aTagEnd}页面重新启用两步验证。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}如需更多帮助，{spanStartTagWithBold}请勿直接回复此电子邮件{spanEndTag}。请在原本的客服表格回复，或在此填写新的客服表格：{aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}罗布乐思支持{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}罗布乐思

english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This message is to notify you that our support team has deactivated 2-Step Verification with Authenticator on your child's Roblox account, {accountName}. This typically occurs due to a support ticket you submitted or as a security measure to ensure the safety of your account. english: Hello {accountName},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This message is to notify you that our support team has deactivated 2-Step Verification with Text Messages for your Roblox account. This typically occurs due to a support ticket you submitted or as a security measure to ensure the safety of your account. A security code will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. You can reactivate 2-Step Verification in your {aTagStartWithHref}{AccountSettingsPageLink}{hrefEnd}account settings{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}If you need further assistance, {spanStartTagWithBold}do not reply to this email{spanEndTag}, and reply to your existing support ticket or submit a new support request here: {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox Support{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox
translation: {accountName} 您好，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我们的客服团队已为您的帐户停用短信两步验证。我们通常会因您提交的客服表格或为了确保您的帐户安全而采取此行动。当登录帐户或进行其他操作时，您将不再需要使用安全代码。您可以在{aTagStartWithHref}{AccountSettingsPageLink}{hrefEnd}帐户设定{aTagEnd}页面重新启用两步验证。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}如需更多帮助，{spanStartTagWithBold}请勿直接回复此电子邮件{spanEndTag}。请在原本的客服表格回复，或在此填写新的客服表格：{aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox 支持{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox

english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This message is to notify you that our support team has deactivated 2-Step Verification with Text Messages on your child's Roblox account, {accountName}. This typically occurs due to a support ticket you submitted or as a security measure to ensure the safety of your account. A security code will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. You can reactivate 2-Step Verification in {aTagStartWithHref}{AccountSettingsPageLink}{hrefEnd}account settings{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}If you need further assistance, {spanStartTagWithBold}do not reply to this email{spanEndTag}, and reply to your existing support ticket or submit a new support request here: {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox Support{aTagEnd}.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox
translation: 您好，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我们的客服团队已为您孩子的帐户 {accountName} 停用短信两步验证。我们通常会因您提交的客服表格或为了确保您的帐户安全而采取此行动。当登录帐户或进行其他操作时，您的孩子将不再需要使用安全代码。您可以在{aTagStartWithHref}{AccountSettingsPageLink}{hrefEnd}帐户设定{aTagEnd}页面重新启用两步验证。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}如需更多帮助，{spanStartTagWithBold}请勿直接回复此电子邮件{spanEndTag}。请在原本的客服表格回复，或在此填写新的客服表格：{aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox 支持{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox

english:
You are about to revert your account to a past state.
To revert your account you must set a new password.
translation:
你即将把帐户还原成之前的状态。
若要还原你的帐户，请先设置一个新的密码。

english: This will reset the following settings:
You are reverting your email to an unverified email.
translation: 你即将把电子邮件还原成未验证的电子邮件。

english: This will disable two step verification.
translation: 这样做将停用两步验证。

english: Create a new password. Do {styleFront}not{styleEnd} use your old password.
translation: 创建一个新密码。请{styleFront}勿{styleEnd}使用旧密码。

description: Subject line for the username reminder email, which provides the user with all of the usernames associated with their email address.
Header in the username reminder email
First part of the username reminder email. This text appears before a list of usernames associated with this email address.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You have requested a reminder for the Roblox accounts associated with this email address. Your accounts are listed below:{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好，{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您已经为与此邮件地址所关联的罗布乐思帐户发出了提醒请求。您的帐户为：{paragraphEnd}

description: Second part of the username reminder email. This text appears after a list of usernames associated with this email address.
translation: {paragraphStart}谢谢您的合作！{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}罗布乐思团队{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer text displayed at the bottom of the username reminder email.
english: You are receiving this email because there has been a request to recover Roblox usernames associated with this email address. If you did not make this request, do not reply to this email directly. Please contact {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}Roblox Support{aTagEnd} and change your password immediately
translation: 因有人请求恢复与此电子邮件地址关联的罗布乐思用户名，您才会收到此封邮件。若不是您本人操作，请不要直接回复此封邮件。请联系{aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}罗布乐思支持{aTagEnd}并立即更改您的账户密码。

description: Informative links displayed at the bottom of the username reminder email. Account safety goes to http://www.roblox.com/info/account-safety and Support goes to http://www.roblox.com/info/help

translation: 显示验证码时出现了一个未知错误。

translation: 尝试次数过多。请稍后重试。

translation: 你当前的密码不正确，密码未更改。

english: Must include new password and confirm password
translation: 必须包含新密码并确认密码

english: Your new password and confirm password must match
translation: 你的新密码须与确认密码相符

translation: 谁可以通过我的手机号码找到我？

english: Too many attempts. Please try again later.
translation: 尝试次数过多。请稍后重试。

translation: 你似乎在尝试使用已更改的用户名进行登录。请使用你的新用户名登录。

english: Your username or password is incorrect. Please check them and try again.
translation: 你的用户名或密码不正确。请检查并重试。

translation: 我们需要确定你不是机器人 :)

english: The words you typed didn't match the picture. Please try again.
translation: 你键入的文字与图片不符。请重试。

english: System error. Please return to login screen.
translation: 系统错误。请返回登录屏幕。

english: You must log in to Roblox to finish authenticating.
translation: 你必须登录罗布乐思以完成身份验证。

translation: 我们无法加载此安全票单。

english: System error. Account could not be restored to this state.
translation: 系统错误。帐户无法恢复至此状态。

translation: 没有与此帐户相关联的电子邮件

english: Sorry, password reset requests expire {expirationHour} hours, {expirationMinute} minutes after issuance. Try requesting another password reset ticket again.
translation: 抱歉，密码重置请求会在发送后的 {expirationHour} 小时 {expirationMinute} 分后过期。请重新提交一张密码重置票单。

english: Check your email for login instructions

帐户状态导致无法重置密码

translation: 如果你在创建帐户时未提供{styleStart}真实的电子邮件地址{styleEnd}，我们则无法向你发送电子邮件。

english: An email with instructions has been sent to you if the email was previously saved on your account.
translation: 如果你的帐户已保存电子邮件地址，那我们已向你发送了一封附有说明的电子邮件。

english: An SMS with your username(s) has been sent to you if the phone number was previously verified on your account.
translation: 如果你的帐户已验证过电话号码，那么我们已向你发送了一条包含你用户名的信息。

english: An error occurred, try again later.
Enter your email to retrieve your username.
translation: 输入你的电子邮件以取回你的用户名。

translation: 输入你的手机号码以取回你的用户名。

description: The "From" field for the password reset email

english:
We noticed that the password changed for your Roblox account: {userName}. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, please click this link to undo the action:
{urlShown}

If you are happy with your new Roblox password, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up. Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page (https://www.roblox.com/help).
translation:
我们注意到你罗布乐思帐户的密码已更改：{userName} 。如果你不想真的更改，或者你认为别人可能不小心作出了此更改，那么请点按此链接以撤销：
{urlShown}

如果你更倾向于使用新的罗布乐思密码，无需任何步骤，帐户已设置好。请不要回复此消息。如果你有任何问题，请查看罗布乐思帮助页面。

english: Sorry, that password cannot be used.

Dear {userName},

We noticed you have changed the password for your account. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, then we need you to contact customer service (https://www.roblox.com/support) to change the password back. That way we will know for sure that your account is secure and safe.

If you are happy with your new password on Roblox, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up.

Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page (https://www.roblox.com/help).
translation:
亲爱的 {userName}，

我们注意到你已更改帐户密码。如果你不是真的想更改，或者你认为别人可能不小心作出了此更改，那么我们需要你联络客户服务以改回原密码。这样，我们才能确认你帐户的安全性。

如果你确定要在罗布乐思上使用新的密码，则无需任何步骤，帐户已设置好。

请不要回复此信息。如果你有任何问题，请查看罗布乐思帮助页面。

description: Email body of verification email that is sent out when an under 13 user adds an email to the account
english: Hello,{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Your child created the account {boldTagStart}{username}{boldTagEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds. Our platform also provides a free development tool called “Roblox Studio” that allows users to create anything they imagine, from simple drag-and-drop building experiences to complex multiplayer games. Millions of kids have used Roblox to imagine what it’s like to create the ultimate theme park, compete as a professional race car driver, star in a fashion show, or simply build a dream home and hang out with friends.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}This email is to inform you that your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent’s email address. The parent’s email address is only used for account management, password resets if the child forgets their password, and to notify parents of changes to the child’s account access. To verify your email address, please click the button below: {lineBreak}{lineBreak}{aTagStartWithHref}{verificationLink}{hrefEnd}{buttonStart}Verify Email{buttonEnd}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}{boldTagStart}About Roblox{boldTagEnd}{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Roblox is dedicated to building an enjoyable, family-friendly environment. If you are happy with your new email address on Roblox, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up.
Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page ({helpLink}).
translation:
亲爱的 {username}，

我们注意到你已将帐户的电子邮件地址从 {oldEmailAddress} 更改为 {newEmailAddress}。如果你不是真的想更改，或者你认为别人可能不小心作出了此更改，那么我们需要你联络客户支持（{supportLink}）以改回原地址。这样，我们才能确认你帐户的安全性。

如果你确定要在罗布乐思上使用新的电子邮件地址，则无需任何步骤，帐户已设置好。
请不要回复此信息。如果你有任何问题，请查看罗布乐思帮助页面{helpLink}。

english:
Dear {username},

We noticed you have changed the email address from {oldEmailAddress} to {newEmailAddress}. If you didn't intend to change it, or you think someone else changed it by mistake, then we need you to contact customer support ({supportLink}) to change the email back. That way we will know for sure that your account is secure and safe.

If you are happy with your new email address on Roblox, you don't have to do anything! It's already set up.
Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please see the Roblox help page ({helpLink}).
translation:
亲爱的 {username}，

我们注意到你已将帐户的电子邮件地址从 {oldEmailAddress} 更改为 {newEmailAddress}。如果你不是真的想更改，或者你认为别人可能不小心作出了此更改，那么我们需要你联络客户支持（{supportLink}）以改回原地址。这样，我们才能确认你帐户的安全性。

如果你确定要在罗布乐思上使用新的电子邮件地址，则无需任何步骤，帐户已设置好。
请不要回复此信息。如果你有任何问题，请查看罗布乐思帮助页面{helpLink}。

english: The Facebook profile url is invalid.
translation: Facebook 个人资料网址无效。

english: The Twitch profile url is invalid.
translation: Twitch 个人资料网址无效。

english: Dear {username},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}We noticed that you have changed your email address from {oldEmailAddress} to {newEmailAddress}. If you made this change, feel free to disregard this email.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}If you did not make this change, or did so by mistake, please click this link to change the email back: {aTagWithHref}{revertAccountEmailLinkWithTicket}{hrefEnd}{revertAccountEmailLink}{aTagEnd}. To keep your account safe, you will be asked to set a new password.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please visit our Help Center.
translation: 亲爱的 {username}，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我们注意到你已将电子邮件地址从 {oldEmailAddress} 更改为 {newEmailAddress}。如果你不想更改，或者你认为别人可能不小心作出了此更改，那么你需要点按此链接{lineBreak}{aTagWithHref}{revertAccountEmailLinkWithTicket}{hrefEnd}{revertAccountEmailLink}{aTagEnd}{lineBreak}以将电子邮件改回原地址。你还将需要输入一个新密码。这样，我们才能确认你帐户的安全性。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}如果你更倾向于在罗布乐思上使用新的电子邮件地址，则无需任何操作，帐户已为你设置好。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}请不要回复此信息，如果你有任何问题，请前往我们的帮助中心。

english: Dear {username},{lineBreak}{lineBreak}We noticed that you have changed your email address from {oldEmailAddress} to {newEmailAddress}. If you made this change, feel free to disregard this email.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}If you did not make this change, or did so by mistake, please click this link to change the email back: {revertAccountEmailLink}. To keep your account safe, you will be asked to set a new password.{lineBreak}{lineBreak}Please do not reply to this message. If you have any questions, please visit our Help Center ({accountHelpLink}).
translation: 亲爱的 {username}，{lineBreak}{lineBreak}我们注意到你已将电子邮件地址从 {oldEmailAddress} 更改为 {newEmailAddress}。如果你不想更改，或者你认为别人可能不小心作出了此更改，那么你需要点按此链接{lineBreak}{revertAccountEmailLink}{lineBreak}以将电子邮件改回原地址。你还将需要输入一个新密码。这样，我们才能确认你帐户的安全性。{lineBreak}{lineBreak}如果你更倾向于在罗布乐思上使用新的电子邮件地址，则无需任何操作，帐户已为你设置好。{lineBreak}请不要回复此信息，如果你有任何问题，请前往我们的帮助中心（{accountHelpLink}）。

english: Hello Roblox user, {lineBreaks}Your username change request has been processed. Your username was changed from {oldUsername} to {newUsername}. If you did not request a username change, seek account help from Roblox Support ({accountHelpLink}). Please do not reply to this email.
translation: 罗布乐思用户您好：{lineBreaks}您的用户名更改请求已通过。我们已将您的用户名从 {oldUsername} 更改为 {newUsername}。如果该请求并非您本人操作，请前往罗布乐思支持页面寻求帐户方面的帮助（{accountHelpLink}）。请不要回复此电子邮件。

english: I am invited to a private server
translation: 我收到了加入私人服务器的邀请

english: This setting controls who can join this user in private servers - servers that can only be joined by invitation of the server owner.
translation: 此设置将控制谁能将此用户加入私人服务器；私人服务器只能在收到服务器主人的邀请后才可加入。

english: Who can invite me to private servers?
translation: 谁可以邀请我加入私人服务器？

description: Subject for email verification email, which is used to let the user confirm that their email address is associated with this roblox account.
translation: 罗布乐思电子邮件地址认证：{username}
罗布乐思电子邮件验证

description: Body text for email verification email. This comes before a button that the user can click to proceed with confirming that they want to associate this email to the given Roblox account.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thanks for choosing to secure your Roblox account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} by providing an email address.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}If you submitted this request, please click the button below to complete the verification process:{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好：{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}感谢您选择为罗布乐思帐户 {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} 提供电子邮件安全认证。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}如果您发送了该请求，请单击下列按钮以完成认证过程：{paragraphEnd}

description: Text on a button in the email verification email. Clicking this button lets the user confirm that they want this email address to be associated with their Roblox account for security purposes.
Second part of the body of the email verification email. This comes after the 'verify email' button.
translation: {paragraphStart}谢谢您的合作！{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}罗布乐思团队{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer displayed at the bottom of the 'email verification' email.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there has been an attempt to verify a Roblox account with your email. If you did not make this request, please disregard this email.
translation: 请不要直接回复本邮件。您之所以会收到本邮件，是因为有人在尝试运用您的电邮地址验证罗布乐思帐户。如果此操作并非您本人执行，请忽略此邮件。

description: Informative links at the bottom of the 'email verification' email.
Subject line for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is sent to the parent of the user, who is responsible for taking action on authorizing the email.

translation: 罗布乐思电子邮件验证

description: First part of the body text for the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is directed at the parent of the user. Below this text is an "I Agree, Verify Email" button that the parent can click to proceed.
english: {paragraphStart}Hello,{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child created the account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} on Roblox, an online entertainment platform that enables kids to imagine, create, and play together in immersive, user-generated 3D worlds.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Your child has provided us with a username, date of birth, and a parent's email address. Please confirm this email address is correct by {emphasisStart}clicking the button below to complete the validation process{emphasisEnd}. Regardless of whether you validate the parental email address or not, the child will still be able to retain their account and chat with others.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}By clicking the "I Agree, Validate Email" button you also agree that (a) You and your child agree to the Roblox {aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}Terms{aTagEnd}, including arbitration, and (b) You will supervise and be solely responsible for your child’s use of Roblox.{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您好：{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您的孩子在罗布乐思上创建了新的账号{emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}。罗布乐思为孩子们提供了可以提升想象力与创造力的线上娱乐平台。不仅如此，您的孩子将可以在用户生成的 3D 世界中与朋友们共同游玩。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}在创建账户时，您的孩子向我们提供了用户名、出生日期及家长的电邮地址。如果您接受账户创建请求，{emphasisStart}请单击下面的按钮完成验证流程。{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}单击“我同意，验证电邮地址”后，即表示您： 一、您与孩子都接受罗布乐思的{aTagStartWithHref}{termsOfServiceLink}{hrefEnd}服务{aTagEnd}及仲裁条款。二、您将会对孩子使用罗布乐思的过程进行监督，并为其游玩时的行为负责。{paragraphEnd}

description: Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('by clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent.

Second part of the body text in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. This is shown after a button that the parent can click to proceed with email verification. 'Parent's Guide to Roblox' and 'Privacy' are paragraph headers.
english: {paragraphStart}You can set your child's safety and parental control settings for their Roblox account at {aTagStartWithHref}{accountSettingsLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSettingsLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Parent's Guide to Roblox{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}We recommend that you visit our Parent’s Guide to help yourself get acquainted with our platform and find helpful tips for creating a positive experience for your kids on Roblox: {aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}You may remove your child's account anytime by contacting customer service at {aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}. Your email will not be used for any other purpose, disclosed to third parties, or combined with any other personal information collected from your child. Please review our privacy policy for more information at {aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}Thank You,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}
translation: {paragraphStart}您可以在{aTagStartWithHref}{accountSettingsLink}{hrefEnd}{accountSettingsLink}{aTagEnd}对您孩子的罗布乐思帐户进行安全与家长管控设置。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Roblox 家长指南{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}我们建议您访问我们的家长指南以帮助您熟悉我们的平台，并找到有用的建议，为您的孩子在罗布乐思上创造积极的体验：{aTagStartWithHref}{parentalPageLink}{hrefEnd}{parentalPageLink}{aTagEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}{emphasisStart}Privacy{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}您可以通过{aTagStartWithHref}{supportPageLink}{hrefEnd}{supportPageLink}{aTagEnd}与客服人员沟通随时注销您孩子的账户。您的电子邮件不会被用于任何其他用途或泄露给第三方，也不会与从您的孩子那里收集的任何其他个人信息绑定。请点击{aTagStartWithHref}{privacyPageLink}{hrefEnd}{privacyPageLink}{aTagEnd}查看我们的隐私政策以获取更多信息。{paragraphEnd}{paragraphStart}感谢您的支持，{lineBreak}{emphasisStart} 罗布乐思团队{emphasisEnd}{paragraphEnd}

description: Footer at the bottom of the 'email verification' email for users under 13.
english: Do not reply to this email directly. You are receiving this email because there has been an attempt to verify a Roblox account with your email. If you did not make this request, please disregard this email.
translation: 请不要直接回复本邮件。您之所以会收到本邮件，是因为有人在尝试利用您的邮箱地址验证罗布乐思帐户。如果此操作并非您本人执行，请忽略此邮件。

description: Links at the bottom of the 'email verification' email for users under 13.

english: When this setting is enabled, the PIN must be provided before changing settings.
translation: 当此设置启用时，变更设置前必须先输入 PIN 码。

english: When this setting is enabled, this account can only access content that is appropriate for all audiences. Additionally, Communication Settings (under the {linkStart}Privacy{linkEnd} page) will be set to Off.
translation: 当此设置启用时，此帐号只能访问老少皆宜的内容。另外，通讯设置（位于{linkStart}隐私{linkEnd}页面下方）将被设为关闭。

english: Parental Controls allow parents to choose the correct settings that will control what experiences their child can access.
translation: 家长管控可使家长选择正确的设置，以控制其子女可获得的游戏体验。

english: This setting controls what type of experiences this user is allowed to visit.
translation: 此设置决定该用户可访问的作品类型。

english: Communication Settings are locked because Account Restrictions (under {linkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} page) are enabled
translation: 由于启用帐户限制（位于{linkStart}安全性{linkEnd}页面下方），“通讯设置”部分已锁定

description: DO NOT TRANSLATE, CAN BE DELETED

translation: 家长 PIN 码已启用
家长 PIN 码已停用

description: Label next to toggle for enabling email-based two step verification.
english: Email codes to confirm your identity
translation: 确认您身份的电子邮件验证码

description: Label next to toggle for enabling authenticator-based two step verification.
english: Retrieve codes from an authenticator app to confirm your identity
translation: 请前往验证 App 获取验证码以确认你的身份。

description: Requirement for enabling authenticator-based two step verification.
Displayed as help text when authenticator-based two step verification is already enabled.
english: Some actions like logging in will require you to enter a code from your authenticator. Check your authenticator app for the code.
translation: 登录帐户或进行其他操作时，你将需要输入验证 App 的验证码。请打开验证 App 以查看验证码。

english: Scan the QR code above into your authenticator app, then enter the generated code below.
translation: 请用验证应用扫描上方的二维码，然后在下方输入生成的验证码。

english: Enter the manual entry key above into your authenticator app, then enter the generated code below.
translation: 请在验证应用中输入上方的手动确认码，然后在下方输入生成的验证码。

description: Message to user for manual Authenticator code entry.
english: Can't scan the QR code? Click here for manual entry.
translation: 无法扫描二维码？点此获取手动确认码。

english: QR code has expired. Please close the modal and try again.
translation: 二维码已过期。请关闭后再重试。

description: The title of the dialog that asks you to input your password before generating recovery codes.
The title of the dialog displaying the newly generated recovery codes.
The description text on the dialog prompting the user to generate new recovery codes by providing their password.
english: Please enter your account password to generate new recovery codes.
translation: 请输入帐户密码以生成新的恢复代码。

english: These are your new recovery codes. Please save them as you will not be able to see the codes again later.
translation: 这是你的新恢复代码。请妥善保存此代码，之后将不会再次显示。

description: Check box confirming the user has saved their recovery codes.
translation: 我已经保存了我的恢复代码

description: A label on the modal for generating new recovery codes  giving notice that the number of remaining unused recovery codes will no longer work.
english: {activeCodeCount} recovery codes will become invalid when new ones are generated.
translation: {activeCodeCount} 恢复代码将在生成新恢复代码后失效。

description: Label next to button for generating two step verification recovery codes.
translation: 生成新的一次性恢复代码。

description: Help text on the two step verification recovery codes section card.
english: If you lose access to your authenticator application, use these to recover your account.
translation: 如果你丢失了验证 APP 的访问权限，请使用此恢复帐户。

english: You need {robuxIcon} {robuxToBuy} more to change your username. Would you like to buy more Robux?
translation: 你还需要 {robuxIcon} {robuxToBuy} 才能更改用户名。是否要购买更多罗宝？

english: To keep you and the community safe, age verification is required to access certain features on Roblox.
translation: 为了确保你和我们社区的安全，只有通过年龄验证的帐号才可以使用部分罗布乐思功能。

description: Label next to toggle after enabling email-based two step verification.
english: Your Account is Protected via Email Verification
translation: 你的帐户受到电子邮件验证的保护

description: Label next to button for generating two step verification recovery codes after two step verification recovery codes have already been generated.
english: Generate new one-time use recovery codes.
translation: 生成新的一次性恢复代码。

description: Message to user that appears after the user has generated recovery codes.
translation: 你有未使用的 {activeCodeCount} 恢复代码。

english: 2-step Verification is required to make further transactions.
translation: 若要继续交易，请完成两步验证。

english: If you change your birthday, your age will no longer be verified.
translation: 如果你更改生日，你的年龄验证将会失效。

description: prompt to add screentime restrictions for children in parental controls
english: You can add restriction hours to your child's account.
translation: 你可以为孩子的帐户添加游戏限制时间。

description: prompt for selecting restriction hours time. ex. "Blocked From 6:00 AM"
prompt for selecting restriction hours time. ex. "Blocked Until 9:00 AM"
prompt for selecting restriction days. ex. "Repeat every Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday"

english: Your time zone has been updated successfully!

description: error shown when user sets screentime restrictions that allow less than 1 hour of playtime
english: People must have at least one hour of allowed time.
translation: 限制时长不得少于一小时。

description: error shown if user inputs a screentime restriction with invalid times (ex 4pm to 10am)
english: Blocked Until time must be later than the Blocked From time.
translation: 限制结束时间必须晚于限制开始时间。

description: prompts a user to update their time zone when stored time zone doesn't match current device timezone
english: Looks like you are in the time zone: {timeZone}, update time zone?
translation: 系统判断你当前的时区为：{timeZone}，是否更新时区？

description: prompts user to save screentime restriction settings
english: Click on Save to update your changes.
translation: 点按保存以保存你的更改。

description: ex. Every Wednesday, Monday, Tuesday. Should include the space after "every" (if this is relevant in translated language)
heading for section where parents can add restrictions to when their children can play Roblox

english: You must select at least one day of the week.
translation: 你必须选择一周中的至少一天。

description: tooltip text for korea screentime controls
english: The Youth Protection Revision Act, commonly known as the Shutdown Law or Cinderella Law, is an act of the South Korean National Assembly which forbids children under the age of 16 to play online video games between the hours of 00:00 and 06:00.
translation: 《青少年保护法》修订案俗称“关机法”或“灰姑娘法”，是韩国国会的一项法案，该法案禁止 16 岁以下的儿童在凌晨 12:00 至早上 06:00 之间进行网络游戏。

description: tooltip label for korea screentime curfew law
english: 12am - 6am is automatically restricted and cannot be edited.
translation: 凌晨 12 点至早上 6 点为自动限制时间，无法编辑。

english: Improve your account security. A code will be required for some actions like logging in.
translation: 提高您的帐户安全性。当您登陆帐户或进行其他操作时，将需要输入验证码。

english: Your username change request has been processed. Your username was changed from {oldUsername} to {newUsername}. If you did not request a username change, please review our account help information at our {startLink}Help Center{endLink}. Please do not reply to directly to this email as replies to this email address are not received.
translation: 您的用户名更改请求已通过。我们已将您的用户名从 {oldUsername} 更改为 {newUsername}。如果该请求并非您本人操作，请前往我们的 {startLink}帮助中心{endLink} 寻求帐户方面的帮助。请不要直接回复此电子邮件，此邮箱无法接收邮件。

description: Make sure that user wants to disable email two step verification when another two step verification method exists.
english: If you turn off 2-Step Verification with Email, a security code from your email will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. Are you sure?
translation: 若关闭电子邮件两步骤验证，您登录或进行部分操作时将不再需要输入电子邮件的验证码。是否确定？

description: Make sure that user wants to disable authenticator two step verification when another two step verification method exists.
english: If you turn off 2-Step Verification with Authenticator, a security code from the Authenticator App will no longer be required for some actions like logging in. Are you sure?
translation: 若关闭验证 App 两步骤验证，您登录或进行部分操作时将不再需要输入验证 App 的验证码。是否确定？

english: You must be at least 18 years old to save screen time restrictions.
translation: 必须年满 18 岁才可以保存使用时间限制。

english: Enabling voice chat will use your microphone input in voice enabled experiences.
translation: 启用语音聊天将在启用语音聊天的作品中使用你的麦克风输入。

english: By clicking 'Verify My Age' you will be completing an ID verification process operated by our third party service provider.
translation: 按下“验证我的年龄”后，你将开始由我们的第三方服务提供商运行的身份验证过程。

Text of the button in the 'email verification' email for users under 13. The text of this button is referred to by name in the first part of the email body ('By clicking "I Agree, Validate Email"...'), so the name should be consistent with

description: Parental spend control launch email, Korean user over 70000 KRW limit
english: {paragraphStart}This email is to inform you that the monthly spend restrictions for account {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd} of {emphasisStart}{amountUsd} USD{emphasisEnd} per month has been changed in accordance with local regulator requirements. These regulations require that accounts held by users under the age of 18 do not spend more than 70,000 KRW per month. As a result, your monthly spend restriction has been updated to {emphasisStart}70,000 KRW{emphasisEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}You can make changes to your monthly spend restriction settings in {parentalControlsLinkStart}Parental Controls{linkEnd} at any time, but you will not be able to remove this restriction or set a limit above 70,000 KRW. For more information on Parental Controls, please visit the {helpCenterLinkStart}Help Center{linkEnd}.{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}Thank you,{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}The Roblox Team{emphasisEnd}

{paragraphStart}我们发送此电子邮件是为了通知您帐户 {emphasisStart}{username}{emphasisEnd}的{emphasisStart}{amountUsd} 
 美元{emphasisEnd}月度消费限制已根据法律法规经过修改。 这些条例规定，18岁以下用户持有帐户的月度消费限制不得超过 7 万韩元。 因此，您的月度消费限制已更新为 {emphasisStart}7 万韩元{emphasisEnd}。{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}{paragraphStart}您可以随时在 {parentalControlsLinkStart}家长控制{linkEnd}中更改您的月度消费限制设置，但您将无法移除此限制或设置超过 7 万韩元的限制。 若要了解多关于家长控制的信息，请访问 {helpCenterLinkStart}帮助中心{linkEnd}。{paragraphEnd}{lineBreak}谢谢您，{lineBreak}{emphasisStart}Roblox 团队{emphasisEnd}

translation: 你将需要 Roblox Premium 以将罗宝兑换为现金。

translation: 当前汇率会应用至所有大于 {minimumDevexRobuxAmount} 罗宝的数额

english: Welcome to the Roblox Developer Exchange!
translation: 欢迎来到罗布乐思 Developer Exchange！

english: The Developer Exchange Program (also known as DevEx) allows you to earn money by creating awesome experiences on Roblox.
translation: Developer Exchange 项目（又名 DevEx）允许你通过在罗布乐思上创造出色的作品来挣钱。

english: Once you earn {minCashoutValue} Robux or more, you are eligible to convert your virtual earnings to real-world cash.
translation: 一旦你挣到 {minCashoutValue} 或更多罗宝，就有资格将虚拟收入转换为现实世界的现金。

english: To use DevEx, you must agree to DevEx Terms of Service and meet the simple requirements set out in those Terms, some of which are as follows:
translation: 要使用 DevEx，必须先同意 DevEx 服务条款，并满足条款中的简单要求，其中包括：
罗布乐思 Premium 订阅；

english: Minimum of {minCashoutValue} earned Robux in your account;
translation: 你的账户中已至少赚取了 {minCashoutValue} 罗宝；
有已验证的电子邮件地址；
有效的 DevEx 平台账户；

english: 13 years of age or older; and
Community member in good standing, having complied with {termLinkStart}Roblox's Terms of Use{termLinkEnd}.
translation: 声誉良好的社区成员，一直遵守 {termLinkStart}罗布乐思的服务条款{termLinkEnd}。

english: You may initiate a request to exchange Robux for cash through the Developer Exchange once each calendar month.Requests are usually processed within 2 - 4 weeks. DevEx conversions are calculated in US Dollars.
translation: 你每月可以请求一次通过 Developer Exchange 请求将罗宝转换为现金。请求通常在 2 - 4 个星期内处理完毕。DevEx 转换以美元计算。

english: When you meet all the requirements, you will see a "Cash Out" button on this page. Click it and follow the instructions to get your payment started.
translation: 当你满足所有需求时，你将在本页上看到一个“取现”按钮。点击并根据说明操作以开始获得你的收入。

english: We recommend that you familiarize yourself with the tax treatment of DevEx payments and the fees associated with different payment methods on DevEx transactions before you cash out.
translation: 在开始取现前，我们建议你先了解一下 DevEx 的税务处理方式以及与各种 DevEx 支付方式有关的手续费用。

english: If your request is approved, and if this is your first time cashing out, you will receive an email inviting you to create an account on our DevEx portal. You will be prompted to enter your information at account creation.
translation: 如果你的请求被通过，且这是你的第一次取现，你将收到一封邮件，邀请你在我们的 DevEx 平台创建帐户。你将在创建帐户时被要求输入你的信息。

english: Please make sure your information is entered accurately into the DevEx portal, and is kept up to date at all times.
translation: 请确保你在 DevEx 平台输入的信息准确无误，且保持更新。

english: The information you provide is used to ensure all payments comply with laws and regulations.  Inaccuracies in information provided could impact your payment.
translation: 你提供的信息用于确保所有支付都符合法律法规。如信息不准确，可能会影响你的支付。

description: heading for what is Roblox section on the landing page
first paragraph under what's Roblox heading on landing page
english: Roblox helps power the imagination of people around the world. As the largest growing social experience platform, over 44 million people come to Roblox every month to create adventures, play games, roleplay, and learn with friends. We call it the ‘Imagination Platform’.
translation: 罗布乐思让全世界的人们展开想象的翅膀。作为不断壮大的社交性体验平台，每月有多达 4400 万玩家来到罗布乐思。不管是创作作品，进行体验，角色扮演，还是与好友一起学习，这个我们称为“想象力平台”的地方欢迎所有人的加入。

description: second paragraph under what's Roblox on the landing page
english: Roblox is the best place to Imagine with Friends. With the largest online user-generated experience platform, and over 15 million experiences created by users, Roblox is the #1 site for kids and teens (comScore). Every day, virtual explorers come to Roblox to create adventures, play games, role play, and learn with their friends in a family-friendly, immersive, 3D environment.
translation: 罗布乐思让你与好友一起展开想象的翅膀。作为最大的用户创作在线体验平台，罗布乐思拥有超过 1500 万个由用户自主创作的作品，这也让美国公司 comScore 认证罗布乐思为儿童及青少年网站的首选。每天都有虚拟探险家前往罗布乐思这个老少皆宜、身临其境的 3D 环境和好友一起学习、玩耍、开启属于他们自己的冒险之旅。

description: first paragraph under Roblox on your device heading on landing page
english: You can access Roblox on all modern smartphones, desktops, Xbox One, Oculus Rift, and soon on Daydream and Cardboard. Roblox adventures are accessible from any device, so players can imagine with their friends regardless of where they are.
translation: 你可以在所有现代智能手机、桌面电脑、Xbox One、Oculus Rift 上访问罗布乐思，不久后还将支持 Daydream 和 Cardboard。你可以从任何设备上加入罗布乐思的冒险历程，无论玩家身在何处，都能与好友一起充分发挥想象力。

description: second paragraph under Roblox on Your Device on landing page
english: You can access Roblox on PC, Mac, iOS, Android, Amazon Devices, and Xbox One. Roblox adventures are accessible from any device, so players can imagine with their friends regardless of where they are.
translation: 你可以在所有 PC、Mac、iOS、Android、Amazon 设备和 Xbox One 上访问罗布乐思。不久后还将支持 Daydream 和 Cardboard。你可以从任何设备上加入罗布乐思的冒险历程，无论玩家身在何处，都能与好友一起充分发挥想象力。

english: Roblox Premium is a {durationType} subscription that costs {costPrice}. Payment will be charged to the iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Roblox Premium will automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged {renewalPrice} for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings.
translation: 罗布乐思 Premium 是{durationType}费用为 {costPrice} 的订阅制度。完成购买时，我们会向您的 iTunes 帐户收取费用。罗布乐思 Premium 为每月自动续订，但如果您目前的订阅期还剩下超过 24 小时，您可以关闭自动续订选项。在您当前订阅期结束前的 24 小时内，我们将会向您的帐户收取 {renewalPrice}。您可以在帐户设置页面管理订阅与自动续订选项。

english: Roblox Premium is a monthly subscription that costs {costPrice}. Payment will be charged to the iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Roblox Premium will automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged {renewalPrice} for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings. If you're under 18 make sure you have the permission of your parent or legal guardian before making a purchase. Making a purchase without permission may result in your account being deleted.
translation: 罗布乐思 Premium 是每个月费用为 {costPrice} 的订阅制度。完成购买时，我们会向您的 iTunes 帐户收取费用。罗布乐思 Premium 为每月自动续订，但如果您目前的订阅期还剩下超过 24 小时，您可以关闭自动续订选项。在您当前订阅期结束前的 24 小时内，我们将会向您的帐户收取 {renewalPrice}。您可以在帐户设置页面管理订阅与自动续订选项。如果您未满 18 岁，在购买前请先征得父母或法定监护人的同意。如果在未获同意的情况下进行购买，可能会导致您的帐户被删除。
订阅 {upsellLinkStart} 以获取更多内容！{upsellLinkEnd}

english: We’ve credited your Roblox credits, but there was an issue processing your Robux grant. Please contact customer support to get your Robux.
translation: 我们已存入您的罗布乐思点数，但在进行罗宝拨款时发生了问题。请联络客户支持部门来取得您的罗宝。

english: There has been an issue processing your Roblox credit. Please try again later!
translation: 处理您的罗布乐思点数时发生了问题。请稍后再试一次！

english: Engagement score and payout based on engagement of monetized users.
translation: 依据有获利的用户参与度而定的参与度评分及支付数额。

english: Premium engagement score is calculated daily based off the amount of time Roblox Premium subscribers spend visiting your experience.
translation: Premium 参与度成绩是根据罗布乐思 Premium 订阅用户在你的作品上所花费的时间，每天计算得出的。

english: Premium engagement Robux earned depends on your Premium engagement score, and is calculated over a 28-day window.
translation: 赚取的 Premium 参与度罗宝取决于你的 Premium 参与度成绩，并以 28 天的时间范围计算。
已获得的 Premium 参与度罗宝

english: Increase Roblox Premium visitors engagement in your experience to earn payouts.
translation: 在你的作品中增加罗布乐思 Premium 订阅用户的体验时间来赚取支付数额。

translation: 你没有资格从 {start} - {end} 期间的玩家那里获得 Premium 支付数额。

english: We're currently experiencing delays. Please check again later.
translation: 我们目前遇到延迟。请稍后再查看。

translation: 在你的作品中增加 {startLink}罗布乐思 Premium{endLink} 订阅用户的体验时间来赚取支付数额。

translation: 待处理赚取的罗宝：${robuxAmount}（基于 {start}-{end} 的 Premium 参与度）

english: Robux Earned: {robuxAmount} (Based on {start}-{end} Premium Engagement window)
translation: 赚取的罗宝：{robuxAmount}（基于 {start}-{end} 的 Premium 参与度）

translation: 待处理赚取的罗宝：{robuxAmount}（基于 {start}-{end} 的 Premium 参与度）

english: The selected date range includes periods ineligible for Premium Payouts.
translation: 选择的日期范围包含不符合 Premium 支付规定的期间。

english: Increase {startLink}Roblox Premium{endLink} visitors' engagement in your experience to earn payouts.
translation: 在你的作品中增加 {startLink}罗布乐思 Premium{endLink} 订阅用户的体验时间来赚取支付数额。
欢迎使用 Premium 支付！

english: Premium Payouts rewards you for making awesome experiences on Roblox that Premium subscribers love. If a Premium subscriber is visiting your experiences, you’re earning a Premium payout, even if the user isn’t spending Robux in your experiences. These payouts are on top of what you earn from selling items in your experience. You can spend your payout on Roblox or you can convert it to cash if you meet the {devexLinkStart}DevEx requirements{devexLinkEnd}.
translation: “Premium 支付”旨在奖励玩家于罗布乐思上制作受 Premium 订户喜爱的超棒作品。如果有 Premium 订户在体验你的作品，即使该用户没有在作品中花费罗宝，你也会获得 Premium 支付。除了在作品中卖出物品的收益，你还能获得这些支付数额。你可以将赚取的款项用于罗布乐思，或是在满足  {devexLinkStart}DevEx 要求{devexLinkEnd}的情况下将其换成现金。

english: To see how much you’ve earned from Premium Payouts, check your {sumLinkStart}Robux history{sumLinkEnd}.
translation: 若要查看你通过 Premium 支付赚了多少，请查阅 {sumLinkStart}罗宝历史记录{sumLinkEnd}。

english: Premium Payouts are calculated per experience based on your Premium Engagement Score. The Premium Engagement Score shows how popular your experience is among Premium subscribers as compared to other experiences. So if Premium subscribers are visiting your experience more than any other experience, your Premium Payout will be higher! You can see what your Premium Engagement Score and Premium Payouts are in {devStatsLinkStart}Developer Statistics{devStatsLinkEnd}.
translation: Premium 支付的数额是根据各作品的 Premium 体验时间成绩来计算。Premium 体验时间成绩显示了您的作品与其他作品相比在 Premium 订阅用户中受欢迎的程度。因此如果和其他作品比起来，Premium 订户更常体验你的作品，你的 Premium 支付数额就会更高！你可以在 {devStatsLinkStart}开发者统计信息{devStatsLinkEnd}中查看自己的 Premium 体验时间成绩和 Premium 支付数额。

english: To increase your Premium Payouts, you can encourage your visitors to buy Premium by building exclusive levels, items, and benefits for Premium subscribers and using the {modalLinkStart}Premium Upsell modal{modalLinkEnd} to allow them to purchase Premium in your experience.
translation: 若想提高 Premium 支付数额，你可以利用以下方式鼓励玩家购买 Premium 会员资格：为 Premium 订户打造专属的关卡、物品和利益，以及使用 {modalLinkStart}Premium 追加销售模态{modalLinkEnd}让他们能在你的作品中购买 Premium 会员资格。

english: To benefit from Premium Payouts, your experience must be free to access.
translation: 若想通过 Premium 支付获益，你的作品需为免费作品。
{moreInfoLinkStart}有关 Premium 支付的更多信息{moreInfoLinkEnd}。

english: Premium Payouts are calculated per experience based on your Premium engagement score. The Premium engagement score shows how popular your experience is among Premium subscribers as compared to other experiences. So if Premium subscribers are visiting your experience more than any other experience, your Premium Payout will be higher! You can see what your Premium engagement score and Premium Payouts are in {devStatsLinkStart}Developer Statistics{devStatsLinkEnd}
translation: Premium 支付的数额是根据各作品的 Premium 体验时间成绩来计算。Premium 体验时间成绩显示了您的作品与其他作品相比在 Premium 订阅用户中受欢迎的程度。因此如果和其他作品比起来，Premium 订户更常体验你的作品，你的 Premium 支付数额就会更高！你可以在{devStatsLinkStart}开发者统计信息{devStatsLinkEnd}中查看自己的 Premium 体验时间成绩和 Premium 支付数额。

english: See how many universe visits are from Premium subscribers.
translation: 查看 Premium 订户的世界访问次数。

english: Premium visits are measured every hour by how many visits are ended by a Premium subscriber.
translation: Premium 访问次数是在计算每小时 Premium 订户的访问次数。

english: Premium visit percentage shows you what proportion of your total visits are from Premium subscribers.
translation: Premium 访问百分比显示的是 Premium 订户在你总访问次数中的占比。

english: Increasing Premium visits helps increase your engagement score, which increases your Premium Payout.
translation: 提升 Premium 访问次数有助于提高你的参与度评分，Premium 支付数额也会因此增加。

english: Increase {startLink}Roblox Premium{endLink} subscribers' engagement in your experience to earn payouts. {learnLinkStart}Learn more{learnLinkEnd}.
translation: 提升作品中 {startLink}罗布乐思 Premium{endLink} 玩家的体验度，即可赚取支付数额。{learnLinkStart}了解更多{learnLinkEnd}。

english: See how often the Premium prompt is shown in your experience and how often someone buys Premium from it.
translation: 查看你的作品中 Premium 提示出现的频率，以及用户由此购买 Premium 会员资格的频率。

english: Impressions are how many times your Premium upsell is shown.
translation: 曝光次数是指 Premium 追加销售显示的次数。

english: Conversions are how many times a visitor buys Premium from your Premium upsell.
translation: 转换次数是指访客通过你的 Premium 追加销售而购买 Premium 会员资格的次数。

english: Increasing your conversion helps increase your engagement score, which increases your Premium Payout.
translation: 提升转换率有助于提高你的参与度评分，Premium 支付数额也会因此增加。

english: Conversion rate is calculated as the proportion of conversions to impressions (# of conversions / # of impressions).
translation: 转换率是根据转换与曝光次数的比例（转换次数 / 曝光次数）来计算。

english: Impressions are how many times your Premium upsell is shown.
translation: 曝光次数是指 Premium 追加销售显示的次数。

english: Premium Payouts are calculated per experience based on your Premium engagement score. The Premium engagement score shows how popular your experience is among Premium subscribers as compared to other experiences. So if Premium subscribers are visiting your experience more than any others, your Premium Payout will be higher! You can see what your Premium engagement score and Premium Payouts are in the {devStatsLinkStart}Premium Payouts chart{devStatsLinkEnd} in Developer Statistics.
translation: Premium 支付的数额是根据各作品的 Premium 互动成绩来计算。Premium 互动成绩显示了您的作品与其他作品相比在 Premium 订阅用户中受欢迎的程度。因此如果和其他作品比起来，Premium 订户更常体验你的作品，你的 Premium 支付数额就会更高！你可以在{devStatsLinkStart}开发者统计信息{devStatsLinkEnd}中查看自己的 Premium 互动成绩和 Premium 支付数额。

english: You don't qualify for Premium Payouts because you have a paid access experience
translation: 你当前不符合 Premium 支付资格，因为你拥有付费作品

english: For the safety and security of your account, your Roblox password has been reset. To regain access to your account, please type in your email or phone number and click the submit button on this page. If you do not have an email or phone number associated with your account, please contact Roblox customer support at {aTagStartWithHref}{emailMailToLink}{hrefEnd}{emailText}{aTagEnd}.
translation: 为了保证你帐户的安全性，你的罗布乐思密码已被重置。若要取回你的帐户，请在此页面输入你的邮件地址或手机号码，并点按“提交”按钮。如果你的帐户没有关联邮件地址或手机号码，请通过{aTagStartWithHref}{emailMailToLink}{hrefEnd}{emailText}{aTagEnd} 与罗布乐思的客户服务团队取得联系。

english: Hello {username},{linebreak}{linebreak}Congratulations! Your experience {gameName} has received a Premium Payout of {robuxAmount} Robux.{linebreak}This payout is calculated every day and reflects how much time Premium subscribers spend playing your experience.{linebreak}To see future payouts, check out the {htmlAHrefStatsPage}Premium tab{htmlCloseAHref} of your experience statistics or the {htmlAHrefMoneySummaryPage}Summary tab{htmlCloseAHref} of your earnings.{linebreak}This is a one-time notification only. If you have other experiences, they may also be earning Robux from Premium Payouts, which will be reflected in their respective experience statistics.{linebreak}Click {htmlAHrefPremiumPage}here{htmlCloseAHref} to learn more about Premium Payouts! {urlPremiumPage}{linebreak}{linebreak}Happy building!{linebreak}- Roblox
translation: 您好，{username}：{linebreak}{linebreak}恭喜！您的作品 {gameName} 收到了一笔价值 {robuxAmount} 罗宝的 Premium 支付。{linebreak}支付数额每日会进行结算，反映了 Premium 会员们在您作品中体验时长。{linebreak}希望查看今后的支付金额时，请前往统计信息中的 {htmlAHrefStatsPage}Premium 标签页{htmlCloseAHref}。同时，也可以从您的收入{htmlAHrefMoneySummaryPage}摘要标签页{htmlCloseAHref}进行查看。{linebreak}本支付提醒只会被推送一次。如果您还有其它作品，或许也会从相关 Premium 支付中获取罗宝。在每个作品的统计信息页面可以查看其收入。{linebreak}点击{htmlAHrefPremiumPage}此处{htmlCloseAHref}可以深入了解有关 Premium 支付的信息！{urlPremiumPage}{linebreak}{linebreak}祝您今后的作品开发顺利！{linebreak}- 罗布乐思团队

english: You must wait {promotionTermNum} days from the time of purchase before canceling your promotional Roblox Premium Builders Club membership. You can then cancel the membership at any time after {promotionTermNum} days. You must cancel before the next renewal date to stop a recurring charge. You will still receive the full time you have previously paid for.
translation: 在您购买罗布乐思 Premium Builders Club会员资格后，需要等待 {promotionTermNum} 天才能取消订阅。{promotionTermNum} 天后，您可以随时取消会员资格。但如果想要避免续订费用，则需在下一个续订周期前取消订阅。取消资格后，您的会员资格仍然会保持至支付时长结束。

english: Your Roblox Premium membership cannot be canceled at this time as it is currently in the process of renewal with our payment processor, which briefly disallows changes to the membership during this time. Once the renewal process is complete, the membership can be canceled and you will still receive the full amount of time paid for. For further information, please contact {linkStart}Customer Service{linkEnd}. Please note, Customer Service is unable to cancel a membership until the renewal process is complete.
translation: 暂时无法取消您的罗布乐思 Premium 会员资格。我们的支付处理商正在处理您的续订，在此期间您将暂时无法变更会员资格。续订完成之后，会员资格即可被取消且仍会保持至支付时长结束。若想进一步对此条例进行了解，请联系{linkStart}客户服务部门{linkEnd}。请注意：客服无法在续订完成之前取消您的会员资格。

english: Premium Payouts rewards you for making awesome games on Roblox that Premium subscribers love. If a Premium subscriber is playing your games, you’re earning a Premium payout, even if the user isn’t spending Robux in your games. These payouts are on top of what you earn from selling items in game. You can spend your payout on Roblox or you can convert it to cash if you meet the {devexLinkStart}DevEx requirements{devexLinkEnd}.
translation: Premium 收益用于奖励受 Premium 用户喜爱的优秀作品。当有 Premium 用户在体验你的作品时，即使该用户没有在作品中花费，你也同样会获得 Premium 收益。这些收益和你在作品中贩卖物品所得的收益是分开的。你可以将这些收益用于在罗布乐思上的消费，如果你满足 {devexLinkStart}DevEx 要求{devexLinkEnd}，还可以进行提现。

english: To see how much you’ve earned from Premium Payouts, check your {sumLinkStart}Robux history{sumLinkEnd}.
translation: 想要了解你的所有 Premium 收益，请查看 {sumLinkStart}历史记录{sumLinkEnd}。

english: To increase your Premium Payouts, you can encourage your visitors to buy Premium by building exclusive levels, items, and benefits for Premium subscribers and using the {modalLinkStart}Premium Upsell modal{modalLinkEnd} to allow them to purchase Premium in your experience.
translation: 要提高 Premium 收益的数额，你可以使用以下方式鼓励访客购买 Premium 会员：为 Premium 用户打造专属关卡、专属物品或专属福利，以及运用 {modalLinkStart}Premium 追加销售模式{modalLinkEnd}，让访客们能在你的作品中直接购买 Premium 会员。

english: To benefit from Premium Payouts, your experience must be a free experience.

{moreInfoLinkStart}有关 Premium 收益的更多信息{moreInfoLinkEnd}。

english: See how many universe visits are from Premium subscribers.
translation: 查看 Premium 订户的世界访问次数。

english: Premium visits are measured every hour by how many visits are ended by a Premium subscriber.
translation: Premium 访问次数代表了每小时有多少访问来自 Premium 订户。

english: Premium visit percentage shows you what proportion of your total visits are from Premium subscribers.
translation: Premium 访问百分比代表了 Premium 订户在总访问次数中的占比。

english: Increasing Premium visits helps increase your engagement score, which increases your Premium Payout.
translation: 提升 Premium 访问次数有助于提高你的活跃度分数，从而增加你的 Premium 收益。

english: Increase {startLink}Roblox Premium{endLink} users' playtime in your experience to earn payouts. {learnLinkStart}Learn more{learnLinkEnd}.
translation: 提升作品中 {startLink}Roblox Premium{endLink} 访客的体验时长，赚取收益。{learnLinkStart}了解更多{learnLinkEnd}。

english: See how often the Premium prompt is shown in your experience and how often a visitor buys Premium from it.
translation: 查看你作品中 Premium 弹窗提示出现的频率，以及访客通过弹窗购买 Premium 会员的频率。

english: Conversions are how many times a visitor buys Premium from your Premium upsell.
translation: 转换次数是指访客通过你的 Premium 追加销售信息购买 Premium 会员的次数。

english: Increasing your conversion helps increase your engagement score, which increases your Premium Payout.
translation: 提升转换率有助于提高你的活跃度分数，从而增加你的 Premium 收益。

english: Conversion rate is calculated as the proportion of conversions to impressions (# of conversions / # of impressions).
translation: 转换率是根据转换与曝光次数的比例（转换次数 / 曝光次数）来计算的。

english: Impressions are how many times your Premium upsell is shown.
translation: 曝光次数是指 Premium 追加销售显示的次数。

english: Premium Payouts are calculated per experience based on your Premium playtime score. The Premium playtime score shows how popular your experience is among Premium subscribers as compared to other experiences. So if Premium subscribers are playing your experience more than any other experience, your Premium Payout will be higher! You can see what your Premium playtime score and Premium Payouts are in the {devStatsLinkStart}Premium Payouts chart{devStatsLinkEnd} in Developer Statistics.
translation: Premium 收益是根据作品的 Premium 体验时长分数来计算的。Premium 体验时长分数显示了在 Premium 会员中，你的作品与其他作品相比受欢迎的程度。因此，如果 Premium 会员更常玩你的作品，你的 Premium 收益就会更高！你可以在开发者统计信息的 {devStatsLinkStart}Premium 收益图表{devStatsLinkEnd}中查看自己的 Premium 体验时长分数和 Premium 收益。

english: You don't qualify for Premium Payouts because you have a paid access game
translation: 你不符合 Premium 收益的要求，因为你的作品需要付费购买
{divOneStart}已赚取：{robuxAmount}{divOneEnd}{divTwoStart}（基于 {start}-{end} Premium 游戏时长范围）{divTwoEnd}

english: ***Note that all data points are updated at 08:00:00.000Z in UTC. This means that if you are in a time zone west of UTC, such as Pacific Time, there can be perceived delays for when data is updated for the next day. Likewise, if you are based in a time zone east of UTC, it may appear that data is being updated at an earlier time. This is because the date filter at the top adjusts to your local time zone but the data points shown below are all in UTC.
translation: ***请注意，所有数据点都会在世界协调时间 08:00:00.000Z 更新。如果你位于世界协调时间以西的时区，如太平洋时区，则第二天更新数据时可能会出现延迟。同样，如果你位于世界协调时间以东的时区，则数据更新时间可能会提前。这是因为上方的日期筛选会根据你的本地时区进行调整，但下面显示的数据点皆以世界协调时间为准。

english: Note: PlayFab is a third party service provider with their own terms and privacy policies. Roblox does not control your use of their services. In order to collaborate with your group editors, you will need to provide collaborators with admin access in PlayFab.

english: Total amount of Robux earned by the experience in a day.
translation: 作品单日赚取的 Robux 总额。

english: The daily revenue breakdown by source, e.g. game shop items, game passes, private servers, paid access, etc.
translation: 各个渠道的单日收入，包括游戏商店道具、游戏通行证、私人服务器及付费通行证等。

english: Avg. revenue per user among all DAUs, measured by Robux, which equals Daily revenue / DAU.
translation: 所有 DAU 中单一用户的平均收入，以 Robux 计算，等于单日收入除以 DAU。

english: Avg. revenue per paying user, which equals Daily revenue / Paying users.
translation: 单一付费用户的平均收入，等于单日收入除以付费用户。

english: % of DAUs are paying users, which equals # of paying users / DAU.
translation: DAU 中付费用户所占百分比，等于付费用户除以 DAU。

english: Breakdown filter does not apply to this chart
translation: 分段筛选不适用于此图表

english: DAU over time can help indicate whether players are consistently engaging with and returning to your game (related to retention). DAU can shift rapidly as a result of new features or content that you release and is a good way to measure the impact of updates on your players.
translation: 单日活跃用户（DAU）趋势可以让你了解玩家是否进行互动并持续回流（与留存率相关）。DAU 可能会因为推出新功能或新内容而改变，你可以通过 DAU 了解你作品的更新对玩家造成的影响。

english: MAU can be maintained or grown by providing regular updates that motivate your players to continue staying in the game and addressing any issues that cause players to leave (such as bugs that cause crashes or buggy states).
translation: 若要维持或增加单月活跃用户（MAU）的数量，你可以定期推出吸引玩家回流的更新内容，并及时处理让玩家离开游戏的问题（例如游戏崩溃以及异常状态等）。

english: Average session time measures how long a user plays each time they visit your game. You can compare it with your expectations based on your game design and genre. Breaking it down by age group, platform, etc. will give you an idea where to iterate your content. It can be used together with D1 retention as an early indicator of your long term retention.
translation: 作为互动性的核心指标，总游戏时间可以帮你了解你游戏的互动程度。如果总游戏时间偏低或者有下降趋势，那么你可能需要查看游戏设计中是否有让玩家过早离开的部分，或检查游戏中是否有其他漏洞。

english: The # sessions and DAU can give you an idea if your game is engaging enough that attracts players to come back multiple times a day.
translation: 会话数量和 DAU 可以帮你判断你的游戏在互动性方面是否有足以吸引玩家单日内多次进入游戏。

english: This metric helps you measure the effectiveness of user acquisition efforts.
translation: 这项指标可以让你测量用户获取的效果。

english: High Day 1 retention often leads to higher overall retention for your game. If your Day 1 Retention is low or drops, that typically means that your new user experience needs to be improved. You might be losing new players early in your game because of confusing tutorials, user interfaces, lack of immediate rewards, or a too-steep immediate progression curve.
translation: 首日的高留存率一般会代表你的游戏有着更高的整体留存率。如果你的首日留存率偏低或者有下降的趋势，你可能需要着手于提高新用户的体验。游戏初期玩家流失的原因可能包括复杂的教程、用户界面、缺少即时奖励、进度曲线过陡等等。

english: Day 7 (D7) Retention is a good metric to track if you are hoping to make your game a daily habit - something they are motivated to play every day. If you have a low D7 retention, this may indicate an issue with engagement (new players aren't motivated to continue playing your game) or progression (players are either completing your content too quickly or taking too long to progress to the next meaningful reward).
translation: 如果你想让玩家习惯每天都来玩你的游戏，那你可以使用 7 天（D7）留存率作为指标。如果你的 D7 留存率偏低，你可以查看下游戏的互动性（新玩家没有动力继续玩你的游戏）或者游戏进度的安排（玩家可能很快就完成了全部内容，或者花费过多时间才能进入下一个有意义的阶段）。

english: D30 retention helps you understand the effectiveness of converting new players to regular players.
translation: D30 留存率可以帮你了解新玩家转换成老玩家的效果。

english: D1 stickiness indicates the overall engagement and retention for both new and returning players who play the game every day. It can be used to understand the impact of your updates.
translation: D1 黏着度代表每天玩你的游戏的新老玩家的互动率和留存率。你可以参照这个指标来了解你作品更新所造成的影响。

english: D7 stickiness can serve as an early indicator of whether your updates lead to long term retention for your overall player base.
translation: D7 黏着度让你可以初步了解你作品的更新对整体玩家群体的长期留存率的影响。

english: D30 stickiness, along with D30 retention, gives a full picture of long term retention for your game.
translation: D30 黏着度和 D30 留存率可以让你全盘了解你的游戏的长期留存率。

english: Revenue, or total Robux earned, is the easiest metric to track for monetization. Knowing how many of your players are willing to pay money in your game and how much your players are willing to spend, among other key metrics, will allow you to understand the health of the monetization in your game and to adjust your monetization strategy more effectively.
translation: 收入，或赚取的 Robux 总额，是最容易追踪的盈利指标。当你了解到游戏中有多少玩家愿意在你的游戏中消费、以及消费具体数额等重要指标时，你就可以更好地掌握游戏盈利制度的好坏，从而更有效地调整你的盈利策略。

english: ARPDAU is one of the key metrics to track for monetization. You can understand the value of each player in your game and use it to estimate the change in revenue you’ll see as your DAU and MAU change over time.
translation: ARPDAU 是盈利的重要指标之一。你可以了解游戏中每一位玩家的价值，并参考这个数字来估算 DAU 和 MAU 的变化对于收入造成的影响。

english: ARPPU focuses on the players who are willing to pay for your game and is most useful when considered alongside your conversion rate. Players who buy something in your game once are often more likely to buy again. A high ARPPU typically means that your paying players are finding high, repeat value in your game and is also indicative of high player engagement.
translation: ARPPU 侧重于愿意在游戏中消费的玩家，当与转换率一起考虑时，这项指标将最能展现其用途。在游戏中消费过一次的玩家很有可能回继续消费。高的 ARPPU 代表付费玩家在你的游戏中能充分体会到回流的价值，同时也代表玩家的互动性较高。

english: Understanding what’s valuable in your game to players can help you figure out what to sell, how to set prices for players with varying wallet sizes, and how to design progression and economy to encourage that first purchase, and then to create longer-term paying users.
translation: 充分了解玩家在游戏中最注重的环节，可以帮你决定该出售什么商品、如何为不同消费能力的玩家设定价格、如何设计游戏进度和经济体系来刺激玩家进行首次消费等等，进而创造更多长期的付费用户。

english: ARPDAU and ARPPU are most useful when considered alongside your conversion rate. Conversion rate reflects how well you are able to motivate players to spend money in your game.  If you have a high conversion rate, for example, and a low ARPPU, that indicates that you are good at getting players to buy at least one item in your game, but that there is little beyond that initial purchase that inspires further spending. Understanding what is inspiring that first-time purchase and examining its value could help you determine what content you need to create to inspire more purchases.
translation: ARPDAU 和 ARPPU 在与转换率一起考虑时最能展现其用途。转换率代表你的游戏可以激励玩家消费的水平。例如，如果你的游戏转换率很高，但 ARPPU 偏低，那么说明很多玩家会在你的游戏中至少购买一样道具，但之后没有继续刺激他们消费的动机。了解了促使第一次消费发生的原因以及价值，你就能更好地判断可以促使玩家继续消费的内容。

english: This metric helps you understand your important revenue driver so that strategically choose the area to optimize for.
translation: 这项指标可以让你找到收入的主要来源，从而判断应该在哪一方面改善。

english: Monetization refers to your ability to earn money from players. The KPIs help you generate actionable insights to optimize your monetization.
translation: 收益代表你从玩家身上赚钱的能力。你可以参考 KPI 指标优化你的收益。

english: The data is net revenue (i.e. after the fees from Roblox and the original creators), does not include refund info, and is delayed by 2 days instead of 1 day for retention and engagement metrics.
translation: 数据指的是净收入（扣去 Roblox 和原创作者的费用后），不包括退款信息，并因留存率和互动指标而延迟 2 天 （而不是 1 天）。
每个用户的平均游玩时间

english: Total play time divided by number of sessions on each day.

Average session time indicates how long a user plays each time they visit your game. You can compare it with your expectations based on your game design and genre. Break it down by age group, platform, etc. will give you an idea where to iterate your content. Use it together with D1 retention as an early indicator of your long term retention.
translation: 这个 KPI 可以帮助你了解玩家的互动情况，在游戏早期作为重点指标提供参考。

english: Percentage of new players in Week0 (D0-D6) who also played at any point during Week1 (D7-D13).
translation: 第 0 周 （D0 - D6）的新玩家百分比（且在第 1 周（D7 - D13）某时间点进入游戏）。

english: W1 (Week 1) Retention is a good metric to track if you are interested in building a more casual game - something that players play on and off over time. Similarly to D7 retention, a low or declining W1 retention can indicate that there are issues with your first-time player experience or initial progression curve.
translation: 如果你的兴趣是打造一个更休闲的游戏（玩家可能会时不时地玩你的游戏），那么 W1 （第一周）留存率对你来说会是一个很好的指标。和 D7 留存率一样，如果你的 W1 留存率较低或持续走低，那么你的首次玩家体验或进度曲线或可能有些问题。

description: The label for average in the chart

english: Congratulations! You are now eligible to activate the new analytics dashboard for your experience, which allows you to see the detailed aggregated metrics, including DAU, Average Session Time, Retention, Stickiness, etc. and break them down by age group, country, etc.
translation: 恭喜！现在你可以为你的作品开启全新设计的数据中心了！你可以在这里看到详细的数据情况，包括 DAU、平均会话时间、留存率、粘性等等。你还可以按照年龄组和国家分组查看。

english: Check out the new analytics dashboard!
The new analytics dashboard has more comprehensive KPIs and detailed breakdowns.
translation: 全新的数据中心将提供更完整的 API 及更详细的分析。

english: You can view your developer products' total sales in daily and monthly stats.

english: We recommend that you enable 2-Step Verification via an authenticator app to make your account more secure. This would help keep your account safe even if your password or email is stolen. If your account is compromised, Customer Support will evaluate the security measures you put in place as we try to help you recover any lost value. Learn more on our {linkStart}help page{linkEnd}.
translation: 为了确保帐户安全，我们推荐您启用身份验证程序进行两步验证。如果您的密码或电子邮件地址被盗，您的帐户将依然会受到保护。如果您的帐户被侵入，客服团队将会在尝试恢复您的帐户信息的同时评估您采取的安全措施。请前往我们的{linkStart}帮助页面{linkEnd}了解更多信息。

english: Hi, {lineBreak}{lineBreak}We recommend that you enable 2-step verification via an authenticator app to make your account more secure. In the event that your account is ever compromised, Customer Support will evaluate the security measures you put in place as we try to help you recover any lost value. {lineBreak}{lineBreak}You can set up an authenticator app on your account by going to {securityPageLinkStart}https://www.roblox.com/my/account#!/security{linkEnd}. {lineBreak}{lineBreak}For more information, please visit our {helpPageLinkStart}help page{linkEnd}.

english: The information collected through the ID verification process will only be used for the purposes of securing your account and/or enabling Roblox features. Roblox is committed to making its websites usable by all people, including those with disabilities by meeting or exceeding the requirements of the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines 2.1 Level A/AA (WCAG 2.1 A/AA).  We strive to make our sites an equal experience for everyone.{lineBreak}We continue to monitor our sites and make sure that all content provided is accessible to all visitors.  In order to help us in this process, we have engaged {linkStart}The Bureau of Internet Accessibility{linkEnd}, an accessibility consulting company, to conduct a full accessibility audit consisting of both automated and manual testing of our websites using BoIA’s A11Y® platform which provides us with specific recommendations that will assist us in ensuring that our Web presence is in conformance with the WCAG 2.1 A/AA.
translation: 罗布乐思致力于通过满足或超过无障碍网页规范 2.1 等级 A/AA（WCAG 2.1 A/AA）的标准，让包括残障人士在内的所有人都可以顺畅使用我们的网站。我们希望所有人都可以在 Roblox 的网站上获得相同品质的体验。{lineBreak}我们会持续观察我们的网站，确保所有访客都可以顺畅使用所有内容。为了达成此目标，我们请了无障碍咨询公司 {linkStart}The Bureau of Internet Accessibility{linkEnd} 为我们进行全面的无障碍审查，包括使用该公司的 A11Y® 平台进行自动和手动测试，并获得符合 WCAG 2.1 A/AA 的相关指导。

english: It is important to note that efforts to the websites are ongoing as we work to implement the relevant improvements to meet WCAG 2.1 A/AA guidelines over time.
translation: 请注意，我们还在持续为了符合 WCAG 2.1 A/AA 而改良我们的网站。

english: While you are visiting our sites, you will notice that we make use of third-party sites such as Facebook, Instagram, Glassdoor, Twitch, YouTube, LinkedIn and Twitter to provide information about Roblox.  Though individuals may have challenges with access to these particular sites, Roblox does not control or remedy the way content is portrayed.
translation: 当你访问我们的网站时将会注意到我们会运用 Facebook、Instagram、Glassdoor、Twitch、LinkedIn、Twitter 等第三方网站提供更多罗布乐思的相关信息。部分人士可能无法顺畅访问所有网站，但罗布乐思无法控制或改善内容的呈现方式。

english: The CPU performs all the calculations needed to run a server. CPU usage is a measurement of how many CPU cores your place is using. The most likely causes of high CPU usage are complex scripts.

english: Server FPS, also known as the tick rate, is the rate of Roblox engine’s core game loop. Likely causes of server FPS dropping include complex scripts, network serialization, physics, and CPU contention on the host.

english: Hi Dev, We received a right-of-erasure-request for the following User ID(s): {{{{UserId}}}} Please delete this User ID immediately from all of your records (e.g. games, data stores, etc.) from the following Game(s): {{{{Places}}}} This is an obligation under data protection laws. If you would like more information about how to delete a User ID from a data store, please visit our Developer Hub at https://developer.roblox.com/articles/Data-store , https://developer.roblox.com/api-reference/class/GlobalDataStore and https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/articles/managing-personal-information. Please note that you must delete the User ID from all of your records, and not just from your data stores. The pages linked above are provided for informational purposes and are not intended to provide a comprehensive method of deleting User IDs. Regards, The Roblox Team
translation: 亲爱的开发者，您好：我们收到了用户 {{{{UserId}}}} 行使抹除权力的请求。请在游戏 {{{{Places}}}} 的所有记录（例如游戏、数据库等）中删除此用户 ID。按照数据保护法律的规定，您必须采取此行动。如果需要更多关于如何在数据库中删除用户 ID 的信息，请访问我们开发者中心的相关链接：https://developer.roblox.com/articles/Data-store , https://developer.roblox.com/api-reference/class/GlobalDataStore 以及 https://developer.roblox.com/en-us/articles/managing-personal-information。除了数据库，您还必须在所有记录中删除此用户 ID。上述链接中的信息仅作为参考，并未完全提供删除用户 ID 的方式。谢谢您，Roblox 团队
